// Stress-test plan (doc/2026-05-03_stress-test-plan.md) — offline_lean
// drivers for E1..E10. Each prove_print emits a `*.prove0.lean`
// file with a Cryptol property as `goal : Prop` and a sorry
// placeholder; the corresponding intTests/test_lean_E<N>_*_proof/
// directory carries the discharge.
//
// SAW's SMT prover will fail/succeed per usual on these — the
// prove_print result is not what we test. What we test is:
//   (1) SAW emits the .lean file with the expected shape (pinned
//       via *.prove0.lean.good).
//   (2) The Lean discharge in intTests/... closes cleanly.

// E1 — bvAdd commutativity over [8]. Baseline one-liner via
// bvAdd_comm. Tier 1.
prove_print (offline_lean "test_offline_lean_stress.E1")
  {{ \(x : [8]) (y : [8]) -> x + y == y + x }};
